{#
/**
 * @file
 * Template for Agent Evaluation tool page.
 *
 * Available variables:
 * - title: Page title
 * - intro: Introduction content
 */
#}
<div class="container py-3">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-11 mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-center mb-3 text-cyan">{{ title }}</h1>
      
      {% if entity_name %}
        <div class="alert alert-success-cyber mb-4 text-center">
          <h4 class="text-cyan mb-2">
            <i class="fas fa-crosshairs me-2"></i>{{ 'Ready to Evaluate'|t }}
          </h4>
          <h3 class="text-white mb-0">{{ entity_name }}</h3>
        </div>
      {% endif %}
      
      <div class="lead mb-4 text-muted-light text-center">
        {{ 'Measure agent capabilities across five fundamental dimensions and 30 sub-dimensions'|t }}
      </div>
      
      <div class="alert alert-info-cyan mb-4">
        <h5 class="text-cyan mb-2"><i class="fas fa-info-circle me-2"></i>{{ 'How It Works'|t }}</h5>
        <p class="mb-2">
          {{ 'This evaluation tool analyzes any agent system—human or machine—across the five dimensions of power: Information Access, Resource Control, Authority & Permission, Network Position, and Synthesis & Application. You provide information about the agent, and the system scores its capabilities on each of 30 sub-dimensions.'|t }}
        </p>
        <p class="mb-2">
          {{ 'The result is an interactive radar chart visualization showing the agent\'s complete power profile, overall capability level (0-9+), and specific strengths, constraints, and limitations.'|t }}
        </p>
        {% if not entity_name %}
        <div class="text-center mt-3">
          <a href="/agent-power-framework/example-entities" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-cyan">
            <i class="fas fa-lightbulb me-1"></i>{{ 'Browse Example Entities'|t }}
          </a>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="mt-5 mb-3 text-cyan text-center">
        <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i> {{ 'Choose Your Evaluation Method'|t }}
      </h2>
      
      <div class="row mb-5">
        <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
          <div class="card card-forseti h-100 hover-lift" style="border: 3px solid #00d4ff;">
            <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
              <div class="mb-3">
                <i class="fas fa-comments fa-4x text-cyan"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-cyan mb-3">{{ 'Chat with Forseti'|t }}</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-light mb-4">
                {{ 'Recommended for most users. Have a natural conversation with Forseti about the agent you want to evaluate. Forseti will ask clarifying questions and automatically score each dimension based on your responses.'|t }}
              </p>
              <div class="mb-3">
                <span class="badge bg-primary me-2">{{ 'Interactive'|t }}</span>
                <span class="badge bg-info">{{ 'Guided'|t }}</span>
              </div>
              <a href="/talk-with-forseti{% if entity_name %}?entity={{ entity_name|url_encode }}{% endif %}" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
                <i class="fas fa-comment-dots"></i> {{ 'Start Chat Evaluation'|t }}
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
          <div class="card card-forseti h-100 hover-lift" style="border: 3px solid #4caf50;">
            <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
              <div class="mb-3">
                <i class="fas fa-edit fa-4x text-success"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-success mb-3">{{ 'Manual Form'|t }}</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-light mb-4">
                {{ 'For experts familiar with the framework. Directly input scores for each of the 30 sub-dimensions using a structured form. Provides complete control over the evaluation process.'|t }}
              </p>
              <div class="mb-3">
                <span class="badge bg-success me-2">{{ 'Direct'|t }}</span>
                <span class="badge bg-secondary">{{ 'Expert'|t }}</span>
              </div>
              <a href="/node/add/evaluated_entity" class="btn btn-success btn-lg">
                <i class="fas fa-list-alt"></i> {{ 'Manual Evaluation Form'|t }}
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="mt-5 mb-3 text-cyan">
        <i class="fas fa-gift"></i> {{ 'What You\'ll Receive'|t }}
      </h2>
      
      <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 g-4 mb-5">
        <div class="col">
          <div class="card card-forseti p-4 h-100">
            <div class="mb-2">
              <i class="fas fa-chart-radar fa-2x text-cyan"></i>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-cyan mb-2">{{ 'Interactive Radar Chart'|t }}</h4>
            <p class="text-muted-light mb-0">
              {{ 'Beautiful visualization of the agent\'s power profile with click-to-expand dimensions showing all 30 sub-dimension scores'|t }}
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="col">
          <div class="card card-forseti p-4 h-100">
            <div class="mb-2">
              <i class="fas fa-clipboard-list fa-2x text-cyan"></i>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-cyan mb-2">{{ 'Detailed Assessment'|t }}</h4>
            <p class="text-muted-light mb-0">
              {{ 'Complete breakdown of scores across all five dimensions and 30 sub-dimensions with explanatory text'|t }}
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="col">
          <div class="card card-forseti p-4 h-100">
            <div class="mb-2">
              <i class="fas fa-layer-group fa-2x text-cyan"></i>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-cyan mb-2">{{ 'Power Level Classification'|t }}</h4>
            <p class="text-muted-light mb-0">
              {{ 'Overall capability rating from Level 0 (No Capability) to Level 9+ (Universal Capability) with detailed profile'|t }}
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="col">
          <div class="card card-forseti p-4 h-100">
            <div class="mb-2">
              <i class="fas fa-search fa-2x text-cyan"></i>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-cyan mb-2">{{ 'Constraint Analysis'|t }}</h4>
            <p class="text-muted-light mb-0">
              {{ 'Identification of specific limitations, biases, and constraints affecting the agent\'s capabilities'|t }}
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="alert alert-warning mb-4" style="border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;">
        <h5 class="mb-2">
          <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> {{ 'Understanding the Heuristic Scale'|t }}
        </h5>
        <p class="mb-2">
          {{ 'The 0-9 scale is a heuristic tool designed for rapid capability assessment. Evaluations require judgment—no automated system can perfectly measure agent power.'|t }}
        </p>
        <p class="mb-0">
          <strong>{{ 'For Level 8+ entities:'|t }}</strong> {{ 'Consider supplementing with quantitative metrics like Net Worth (Resource Control), Data Asset Valuation (Information Access), Approval Rating (Authority), Network Reach (Network Position), or AI Benchmarks (Synthesis).'|t }}
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center mb-4">
        <a href="/agent-power-framework" class="btn btn-outline-cyan btn-lg">
          <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> {{ 'Learn About the Framework'|t }}
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
